summary: An ordinance granting to Puget Sound Traction, Light & Power Company, its successors and assigns, the right and authority to construct, maintain and operate a freight spur from a connection with the existing tracks of Puget Sound Traction, Light and Power Company, at Latona Avenue and East 65th Street, easterly along East 65th Street and crossing 4th Avenue Northeast, to block 87, Woodlawn Addition to Green Lake.
